# ALX Project 0x14

## API Overview
The MoviesDatabase API provides access to movie, TV, and celebrity data.  
It includes details such as titles, genres, ratings, release dates, cast & crew, and more.  
You can search for movies, retrieve trending lists, or get detailed information about specific titles or people.

## Version
v1 (as per API documentation)

## Available Endpoints
- **/titles** – Search for movies or TV shows by title.
- **/titles/{id}** – Get details for a specific movie or TV show.
- **/titles/random** – Retrieve a random movie or TV show.
- **/actors/{id}** – Get details for a specific actor.
- **/genres** – List all available genres.
- **/trending** – Get trending movies or TV shows.

## Request and Response Format
**Request Example:**
```http
GET https://moviesdatabase.p.rapidapi.com/titles
Headers:
  X-RapidAPI-Key: YOUR_API_KEY
  X-RapidAPI-Host: moviesdatabase.p.rapidapi.com
